<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Atendimento iniciado</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0;background:#F5F5F5;color:#262123;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#F5F5F5;padding:24px 12px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="max-width:680px;background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;">
            <tr>
              <td style="background:#D90C2C;color:#FFFFFF;padding:24px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;">Portal de Abatimentos Tirol</p>
                <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:24px;line-height:1.25;">Atendimento iniciado para o abatimento #<%= abatimento.id %></h1>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:24px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">A sua solicitacao de abatimento foi recebida e entrou em atendimento pela nossa equipe.</p>

                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="margin-bottom:20px;">
                  <tr>
                    <td width="50%" style="padding-right:6px;">
                      <div style="border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:10px;padding:16px;background:#FFFFFF;">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 6px;color:#6B7280;font-size:13px;">Total em devolucoes</p>
                        <p style="margin:0;color:#19743A;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;"><%= totals.devolucoes %></p>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                    <td width="50%" style="padding-left:6px;">
                      <div style="border:1px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:10px;padding:16px;background:#FFFFFF;">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 6px;color:#6B7280;font-size:13px;">Status</p>
                        <p style="margin:0;color:#262123;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;">Em atendimento</p>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <p style="margin:0 0 18px;color:#6B7280;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;">Quando o boleto estiver disponivel, voce recebera um novo aviso e podera baixa-lo pelo portal.</p>

                <a href="<%= portal_url %>" style="display:inline-block;background:#D90C2C;color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;">Acompanhar solicitacao</a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
